NEGATION
OPERATOR
OP_CLASS
PARAM
POST_ANNOTATION
QUERY
QUERY_FALLBACK
RIGHT
RULE
SEN
STATEMENT
TAG
TARGET
TRANSFORM
TYPE_INSTANCE
VALUE


